Run the activate_dotfiles script to create symlinks
in my home directory back to the actual dot files in
the dot_files/ directory.

Create new or update existing dot files. Then...
o git remote add origin https://github.com/brianthomson42/dot_files.git  # 1st time
o git push -u origin master  # all subsequent updates

To set up dot files on new machine...
o git clone https://github.com/brianthomson42/dot_files.git
o ./activate_dotfiles

Note: the running of git clone and activate_dotfiles is deprecated via the use of Puppet.
